OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThames Water says staff    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fenduring abuse from public 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thames Water has said its staff members
OL,6, have been through "challenging times"  
OL,7, recently, becoming the target of verbal
OL,8, and physical abuse.                    
OL,10,FOne of the company's directors, Tess   
OL,11,FFayers, met with the BBC at its sewage 
OL,12,Ftreatment works in Burford,            
OL,13,FOxfordshire.                           
OL,15,FThe water provider has come under      
OL,16,Ffierce criticism for sewage spillages. 
OL,18,FMs Fayers said every person in her team
OL,19,F"comes to work to do the best possible 
OL,20,Fjob they can".                         
